3. Cross-profile generalization heatmap (the 4x4 matrix as a figure).
4. For PLC specifically: a before/after time-series plot over samples 38150-38250 comparing v1 GRU prediction vs per-profile PLC GRU prediction vs truth. This is the direct visual test of whether the dilution hypothesis explains idx=38180.

